			This entry was posted in <a href="https://upstarthr.com/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a> and tagged <a href="https://upstarthr.com/tag/candidate-experience/" rel="tag">Candidate Experience</a>, <a href="https://upstarthr.com/tag/recruiting/" rel="tag">Recruiting</a>, <a href="https://upstarthr.com/tag/talent-acquisition/" rel="tag">Talent Acquisition</a> on <a href="https://upstarthr.com/3-candidate-experience-trends-you-should-know/" title="8:07 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2019-01-22T08:07:41+00:00">January 22, 2019</time></a><span class="by-author"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://upstarthr.com/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Ben" rel="author">Ben</a></span></span>.								</footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
